					<br>
					• Answer any questions posed by students to the internal messaging board (Ed Discussion).
				</p>
				<br>
				<h5>
					Real-Time Technology Solutions (New York, NY)
				</h5>
				<i> July 2016 - September 2019</i>
				<p>
				• Use IBM's Rational Functional Tester to test software at various clients in the metropolitan area. 
				<br>
				• Work on the internal IT team as an engineer tasked with demoing the company's proprietary software to prospective clients as well as debugging and resolving bugs. 
				<br>
