				</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<h5> Georgia Institute of Technology (Atlanta, GA)</h5>
					<i> Master of Science, Computer Science 
						<br>
						Concentration: Interactive Intelligence
					</i>
